TROUT MINING COMPANY, Appellant, v. George DUCICH, Appellee. No. 6452. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 1, 1931.

Before SAWTELLE, Circuit Judge, and KERRIGAN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal in above cause dismissed; mandate forthwith.
